==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Honey from the mouth, a sword from the belly.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: kŏu mì fù jìan

===Phrase===
'''[[口]][[蜜]][[腹]][[剑]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Sweet words, but a wicked heart.

===Alternate forms===
[[口]][[密]][[腹]][[劍]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

